This is a list of Shikinaisha in [[Satsuma Province]]. That is the shrines in the [[Engishiki Jinmyōchō]] in the province.

The Engishiki Jinmyōchō counts 2 Shikinaisha in the province – 2 Shikinai Shosha and 0 Shikinai Taisha.

